# Configuration Rules for WDIO Starter

## Configuration Structure

1. Organize configuration files by environment
2. Use TypeScript for type safety
3. Document configuration options
4. Keep configuration files DRY
5. Use environment variables for sensitive data

## Configuration Best Practices

1. Avoid hardcoded values
2. Use default values where appropriate
3. Document changes to configuration
4. Keep configuration files up to date
5. Review configuration for security issues 